Package com.timebuddy.models

package com.timebuddy.models
This package contains the model classes representing the core entities of the application. Models such as Todo, TodoList, User, MonthlyEvent, Day, and others are used to represent and store data within the system. The model classes are designed for persistence with the database using JPA annotations. These models are used in the business logic and are transferred between the controller and service layers.
